{"tid":1839523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線醫護人員 唔罷工你點對得住香港人？","createTime":"2020-01-24T12:50:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T14:06:25.000Z","uid":203873,"like":64,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"fb90a6c687f9bacad4288ab789ee6c3c5df57a82","tid":1839523,"uid":203873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:50:32.000Z","msg":"淨係諗自己罷工會對唔住其他唔敢罷既人<br />\n有冇諗過 你地罷工<br />\n係其他唔敢罷既人最大既動力？<br />\n最好pm啲醫護朋友 叫埋佢地一齊罷<br />\n捉住政府個春袋大大力揸落去<br />\n到時一更得翻幾個<br />\n龐大既工作量 唔罷都要焗住罷<br />\n<br />\n用香港人既資源 用你既學歷技術<br />\n為支那狗賣命？<br />\n佢地係會除你口罩<br />\n向你吐口水既社會垃圾<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔罷？<br />\n你對唔對得住香港人。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"e618bdf8676063e72ca08ae8614c820cf0a8ddc1","tid":1839523,"uid":203873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:51:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ecca30d5e457f5f8f00588faf79b528439456fd","tid":1839523,"uid":162008,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:51:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"95577beca146fa0232a1c67b2091e7fb83ec0b36","tid":1839523,"uid":203873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:52:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a8b23705ca1602f8c27331d2476d9aefebc2ebc","tid":1839523,"uid":203873,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:52:50.000Z","msg":"我絕不與罷工前線醫護割蓆"},{"pid":"86f41c06f0540883327200c0baa7c5d133bceb95","tid":1839523,"uid":52911,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21